PAuFtjha","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec3YFfJMzzElQguf","target":"recv0dAY2ULzJ687g","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec3YFfJMzzElQguf","target":"recOdl9oB4UWmbiqP","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec3YFfJMzzElQguf","target":"recfrXyxhuYOczKTm","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec3YFfJMzzElQguf","target":"recQNOLYAluyoB3WG","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec3YFfJMzzElQguf","target":"recbzTNkxyES3LbQF","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec3YFfJMzzElQguf","target":"recjkmUO88wihv8Ci","label":"event"},{"source":"rec3YFfJMzzElQguf","target":"recc78JIsfuTy7cNu","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"recvbhVHwgVjBMJpc","ref":"Exod.12.1","text":"And the LORD spake unto Moses and Aaron in the land of Egypt, saying,"},{"id":"recGlrsR7MPRp3wZy","ref":"Exod.12.2","text":"This month shall be unto you the beginning of months: it shall be the first month of the year to you.","year":-1491},{"id":"recubj2rdlsev8O4W","ref":"Exod.12.3","text":"Speak ye unto all the congregation of Israel, saying, In the tenth day of this month they shall take to them every man a lamb, according to the house of their fathers, a lamb for an house:","year":-1491},{"id":"recG9UI2M02SsrIGg","ref":"Exod.12.4","text":"And if the household be too little for the lamb, let him and his neighbour next unto his house take it according to the number of the souls; every man according to his eating shall make your count for the lamb.","year":-1491},{"id":"recqsIoblbgj0TYzj","ref":"Exod.12.5","text":"Your lamb shall be without blemish, a male of the first year: ye shall take it out from the sheep, or from the goats:","year":-1491},{"id":"recgX38tS1TmeXtMV","ref":"Exod.12.6","text":"And ye shall keep it up until the fourteenth day of the same month: and the whole assembly of the congregation of Israel shall kill it in the evening.","year":-1491},{"id":"recJBc54Tmaghxlfy","ref":"Exod.12.7","text":"And they shall take of the blood, and strike it on the two side posts and on the upper door post of the houses, wherein they shall eat it.","year":-1491},{"id":"recs0BRiM08lnE5Em","ref":"Exod.12.8","text":"And they shall eat the flesh in that night, roast with fire, and unleavened bread; and with bitter herbs they shall eat it.","year":-1491}]}
